::Reptilica/Bloodystrike::

Reptilica and Bloodystrike enter the Alliance base, carrying the femmbot with 
them. Her shivers were exciting both of them, each one fighting to get hold 
of more of her.

Bloodystrike growls. "You're hogging her!" he comlains, adjusting the female 
so that more of her would be touching him.

"I'm hoggin' her?!" Reptilica exclaims, tugging the female to place more of 
her weight on him, "You're the one hoggin'!"

Bloodystrike sighs, turning his head to admire the femm's curves. Reptilica 
growls, activating his comm-link.

"Zardus," he says into it, "We have an unconscious femm here. Where do we put 
her?"
